Summary: Blue UFO spinning above house in Yakima WA
trends: There have been 15 other sightings in Yakima
There was one other sighting in Yakima on or around August 31st 2009
This sighting has never been favorited.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt around 1am, me and my boyfriend went outside to go to the store and I noticed very blue spinning light high in the sky (slightly bigger than the size of a star). I went back inside to grab my camera and took some pics. I went to the store and came back 20 minutes later and it was still there. After an hour of looking at it, I went inside. I have no idea how long it had actually been there or when it left.
